Type: Package
Package: distiller
Title: Distill Environmental Public Health Tracking Network Data Down to XML
Version: 0.4.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Alexander", "Senetcky", , "asenetcky@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0009-3730-5397"))
Description: Convert dataframes of environmental public health tracking data
    into XML files that are compliant with the Centers for Disease Control 
    and Prevention's (CDC) Environmental Public Health Tracking Network's (EPHT)
    data submission process. Users can also quickly validate their submission's 
    data and metadata to reduce repeat visits to the time-consuming
    test submission portal.
